Password Generator

bookmark_border
  • subject UI / UX
Description

Create a Password generator using following details:-

  • There should be only one CENTER tag contains:-
  1. H1 tag with text "Password Generator".
  2. An empty LABEL tag with ID result below H1 tag.
  3. TABLE tag with 6 TR tags contains:-
  4. Each ROW contains two TD tags.
  5. First row 's, first column contains LABEL tag with text "Password Generator".
  6. First row's second column contains SELECT tag with ID length contains following OPTIONS :-
  7. OPTION 8, VALUE 8
  8. OPTION 16, VALUE 16
  9. OPTION 32, VALUE 32
  10. OPTION 64, VALUE 64
  11. OPTION 128, VALUE 128
  12. OPTION 256, VALUE 256
  13. Second row's first column contains LABEL tag with text "Include Symbols:".
  14. Second row's second column contains INPUT tag with ID symbols and TYPE must be CHECKBOX.
  15. Third row's first column contains LABEL tag with text "Include Numbers:".
  16. Third row's second column contains INPUT tag with ID numbers and TYPE must be CHECKBOX.
  17. Fourth row's first column contains LABEL tag with text "Include Lowercase Characters :".
  18. Fourth row's second column contains INPUT tag with ID lower-case and TYPE must be CHECKBOX.
  19. Fifth row's first column contains LABEL tag with text "Include Uppercase Characters:".
  20. Fifth row's second column contains INPUT tag with ID upper-case and TYPE must be CHECKBOX
  21. Six row's first column contains BUTTTON tag with ID generate-button and TEXT must be "Generate Password".
  22. Six row's second column contains BUTTON tag with ID clear-button and TEXT must be "Clear".

Workflow :-

  • INITIALLY all CHECKBOX must be UNCHECKED.
  • INITIALLY SELECT must have FIRST VALUE selected.
  • After CLICKING on the Generate Password button the following things should happen:-
  1. If no any checkbox is checked than there should be an error "!Please select at least one checkbox." show in LABEL (with ID result).
  2. If checkbox is selected than generate password and show it on LABEL (with ID result).
  • After CLICKING on the Clear button the following things should happen:-
  1. All CHECKBOX must be UNCHECKED.
  2. SELECT option changed to First option.
  3. LABEL (with ID result) should be EMPTY.
